long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Kids grow up fast. You end up with your storage spaces filled with items that are not being used anymore. But still, they are in very good condition, so you don't want to throw them away either. At the same time you need to get your kids a whole bunch of bigger clothes, larger sports equipment and more advanced toys. Swap.com Valet Service is the smartest way to do that! 

1. Send items to Swap.com Valet Service
Just pack your kids' items and get them out of the house immediately

2. Valet Service
We photograph, store and list your items on the service for you. You set the sales price. 

3. Get Items or Money
Receive money for your items or other items you're interested in.

Benefits:
- Good-looking photos sell
- You spend no time listing your items
- You have full control of your online item listings
- Listed items can be sold, swapped or returned to you
